---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Hospital Financial Assistance Request Letter — LoopholeDB"
  description="Free fill-in-the-blank letter requesting a hospital's financial assistance program (charity care) application under IRC § 501(r). Print or save as PDF."
>
  <Nav />
  <main>
    <div class="template-toolbar no-print">
      <div class="toolbar-inner">
        <a href="/us/have-medical-bills/hospital-charity-care" class="toolbar-back">← Hospital Charity Care</a>
        <div class="toolbar-actions">
          <p class="toolbar-hint">Fill in the <mark>[BRACKETED FIELDS]</mark>, then print or save as PDF.</p>
          <button onclick="window.print()" class="btn btn--primary">Print / Save as PDF</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-wrap">
      <article class="document">

        <div class="doc-sender">
          <p>[YOUR FULL NAME]</p>
          <p>[YOUR STREET ADDRESS]</p>
          <p>[CITY, STATE, ZIP CODE]</p>
          <p>[YOUR PHONE NUMBER]</p>
          <p>[YOUR EMAIL ADDRESS]</p>
        </div>

        <p class="doc-date">[DATE]</p>

        <div class="doc-recipient">
          <p>Patient Financial Services</p>
          <p>[HOSPITAL NAME]</p>
          <p>[HOSPITAL MAILING ADDRESS]</p>
          <p>[CITY, STATE, ZIP CODE]</p>
        </div>

        <p class="doc-re"><strong>Re: Request for Financial Assistance Application — Account / Patient Number: [ACCOUNT OR PATIENT NUMBER]</strong></p>

        <p>Dear Patient Financial Services Representative:</p>

        <p>
          I am writing to formally request a Financial Assistance Program (FAP) application for the medical services I received at [HOSPITAL NAME] on or around [DATE(S) OF SERVICE]. I understand that, as a nonprofit hospital operating under § 501(c)(3) of the Internal Revenue Code, [HOSPITAL NAME] is required by IRC § 501(r) and 26 CFR § 1.501(r)-4 to maintain a written Financial Assistance Policy and to make FAP applications available to patients who may qualify.
        </p>

        <p><strong>Account Information</strong></p>
        <table class="ref-table">
          <tr><td>Patient Name:</td><td>[YOUR FULL NAME]</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Date(s) of Service:</td><td>[DATE(S) OF SERVICE]</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Account / Bill Number:</td><td>[ACCOUNT OR BILL NUMBER]</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Total Amount Billed:</td><td>$[AMOUNT BILLED]</td></tr>
        </table>

        <p><strong>Basis for This Request</strong></p>
        <p>
          I believe I may qualify for financial assistance based on my household income and current financial circumstances. I respectfully request that you:
        </p>
        <ol>
          <li>Provide me with a copy of the hospital's current Financial Assistance Policy (FAP) and the plain-language summary;</li>
          <li>Provide me with a completed FAP application form; and</li>
          <li>Place a hold on any collection activity, including referral to a collection agency or reporting to credit bureaus, while my application is under review, as required by 26 CFR § 1.501(r)-6.</li>
        </ol>

        <p><strong>Income and Household Information</strong> (to assist with initial screening)</p>
        <table class="ref-table">
          <tr><td>Household Size:</td><td>[NUMBER OF PEOPLE IN HOUSEHOLD]</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Approximate Annual Household Income:</td><td>$[APPROXIMATE ANNUAL INCOME]</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Insurance Status:</td><td>[UNINSURED / INSURED — name of insurer and remaining balance after insurance]</td></tr>
        </table>

        <p>
          I am prepared to provide documentation of my income and financial situation, including [check all that apply]:
        </p>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>☐ Most recent federal tax return (Form 1040)</li>
          <li>☐ Recent pay stubs (last 2–3 months)</li>
          <li>☐ Proof of government assistance (Medicaid, SNAP, SSI, etc.)</li>
          <li>☐ Unemployment benefit statement</li>
          <li>☐ Bank statements</li>
          <li>☐ Other: [DESCRIBE]</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          Please contact me at the phone number or email address above to advise me of next steps or to request any additional documentation. I am committed to resolving this balance and appreciate your assistance.
        </p>

        <p>Sincerely,</p>

        <div class="doc-sig">
          <div class="sig-line"></div>
          <p>[YOUR PRINTED NAME]</p>
        </div>

        <p class="doc-enclosures"><strong>Enclosures:</strong> [List any income documentation included with this letter]</p>

        <div class="doc-footer-note no-print">
          <p><strong>Tips:</strong> Send via certified mail and keep a copy. Under IRC § 501(r)-6, the hospital cannot take "extraordinary collection actions" (lawsuits, wage garnishment, credit reporting) until it has made reasonable efforts to notify you of the FAP and given you time to apply — typically 120 days from the first billing statement. If the hospital refuses to provide an application or continues collection activity, file a complaint with the IRS (Form 13909) and your state Attorney General's office.</p>
        </div>

      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
  <div class="no-print"><Footer /></div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .template-toolbar {
    background: var(--color-espresso);
    padding: 0.85rem 0;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 10;
  }
  .toolbar-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .toolbar-back {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(242,235,224,0.6);
    transition: color var(--transition);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .toolbar-back:hover { color: var(--color-cream); }
  .toolbar-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .toolbar-hint {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: rgba(242,235,224,0.55);
  }
  .toolbar-hint mark {
    background: rgba(242,235,224,0.15);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 0.1em 0.3em;
  }

  .doc-wrap {
    background: var(--color-cream-dark);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 5rem;
  }

  .document {
    background: #fff;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding: 3.5rem 4rem;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #111;
  }

  .document p { margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }

  .doc-sender { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .doc-sender p { margin: 0; line-height: 1.55; }

  .doc-date { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  .doc-recipient { margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
  .doc-recipient p { margin: 0; line-height: 1.55; }

  .doc-re { margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }

  .ref-table {
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .ref-table td {
    padding: 0.2rem 1rem 0.2rem 0;
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  .ref-table td:first-child {
    color: #555;
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-style: italic;
    min-width: 200px;
  }

  .document ol {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }
  .document ol li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  .document ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }
  .document ul li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }

  .checklist { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
  .checklist li { padding-left: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  .doc-sig {
    margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .sig-line {
    width: 260px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #888;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .doc-enclosures { font-size: 0.9rem; }

  .doc-footer-note {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: #f5f0e8;
    border-left: 3px solid #b08860;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #555;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }
  .doc-footer-note p { margin: 0; }

  @media print {
    .no-print { display: none !important; }
    .doc-wrap { background: #fff; padding: 0; }
    .document { box-shadow: none; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 100%; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .document { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
    .toolbar-inner { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .ref-table td:first-child { min-width: 140px; }
  }
</style>
